description: Django miscellaneous - module with different useful stuff for django. Here youll find - couple decorators, like render_to and receive - json_encode module for simplify work with json - some usefull templatetags, like set, filter, get etc some additional utilities - bbcode template tags - template tags that provide like and share for social sevices.
